# Course data

## Unit files

- Location: `src/data/course/units/unit-N-<slug>.ts`
- Export with `satisfies CourseUnit`; register in `src/data/course/index.ts`
- IDs: `unit-N`, words `{wordId}`, sentences `unit-N-s-N`, MC questions `unit-N-mc-N`

## Unit fields

```ts
export const unitNGreetings = {
  id: "unit-1",
  unitNumber: 1,
  title: "Greetings",
  icon: Sun,                    // lucide-react
  iconBgClass: "bg-amber-100",
  iconColorClass: "text-amber-600",
  words: [...],                 // CourseWord[]
  practiceSentences: [...],     // for "sentence" activity
  multipleChoiceQuestions: [...], // GameQuestion shape, 4 options
  typedAnswerQuestions: [...],  // for "complete-sentence" activity
} satisfies CourseUnit;
```

## Activities

Activity IDs and metadata live in `src/data/course-activities.ts`. Background images: `/map/<activityId>.png` (override in `getCourseActivityBackgroundUrl`).

| Activity ID | Data source |
|-------------|-------------|
| `flashcards`, `write`, `matching` | `unit.words` |
| `sentence` | `unit.practiceSentences` |
| `multiple-choice`, `spell` | built from unit via `buildMcTopic` / `buildSpellTopic` |
| `complete-sentence` | `unit.typedAnswerQuestions` |

## Question content

- MC: reuse `GameQuestion` — short sentences, exactly four options, `correctIndex` 0-based
- Typed answer: `CourseTypedAnswerQuestion` with `prompt`, `textBefore`, `textAfter`, `answer`, `imageUrl`
- Include Vietnamese `translation` on `CourseWord` entries
